## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="33cab-285">Das folgende Beispiel zeigt die <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> und <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> Eigenschaften der <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> Klasse.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33cab-285">The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> properties of the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33cab-286">In diesem Beispiel wird der vom Benutzer angegebene <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> und <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> aller seiner <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33cab-286">This example gets the user-specified <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> of all its <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>.</span></span>  
  
